It is a length ball around off, Green plants his front foot outside the line of off and tries to defend with bat close to the pad. It surely hits the front pad. A huge appeal but turned down. Pakistan review but Ultra Edge shows there is an inside edge.
FOUR BYES! Down the leg side, Smith looks to sweep but misses. It straightens and hence, goes past the keeper for a boundary in the fine leg region.
On middle, defended.
Tossed up on off, this is pushed to mid off.
Floats it up on off, Smith leans forward and keeps it out.
Slower through the air and lands it on middle, Smith plays it to covers.
Fuller and on off, Smith pushes it to mid off.
Angled into middle, this is worked towards wide mid on for one.
Good length and on off, Smith pushes it to covers.
Angled into the pads, this is worked through square leg for one.
A bumper, Green ducks under it.
A single now as this is worked through mid-wicekt.

Fifty for Smith! Another superb knock from one of the best in the world! He though has not been converting his fifties into big scores lately but has a chance here. Can he do so? There are three batters before him who have got to fifty but haven't converted it into a ton. He gets there with a controlled pull through square leg for one.
Tossed up on middle, defended.
Loopy ball on off, blocked.
Tossed up on off, Smith pushes it back to the bowler.
Flatter and on off, Smith defends.
Tosses it up on middle, Steven Smith lunges and keeps it out.
Well bowled! The arm ball to end, Smith looks to defend, it goes off the inner half on the leg side.
On a length and around off, defended.
Shot! Just a push! Shorter and on off, this is pushed through covers for three.
Angled into the pads, Smith works it to mid-wicket.
Length again and on off, Smith comes forward and keeps it out.
That is nicely played in the end! Outside off, Smith waits and then guides it past point for two.
On off, defended.
Tossed up, around off. Green prods and pushes it towards cover.
Nicely done! Floated, on a length, outside off. Green waits for the ball to turn and then guides it through the third man region. Fawad Alam cuts it off and the batters take three runs.
Flatter ball, on off. Steven Smith blocks it out.
Slower through the air, around off. Steven Smith gets forward and defends it.
Another loopy ball, full and just outside off. Smith gets to the pitch of the ball and keeps it out.
Tosses it up, around off. Smith blocks it solidly off the front foot.
Flatter ball, on middle. Cameron Green stays back to block it onto the deck.
Floated, full and on middle. Cameron Green prods and tucks it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, around middle. Cameron Green keeps it out.
Floated, full and on middle. Cameron Green gets forward and eases it to mid on.
A bit quicker, on a length, around off. Cameron Green keeps it out off the back foot.
A loopy ball, outside off. Green skips down the track and yorks himself in the process. He digs it out back to the bowler.

FOUR! Excellent use of the feet and Smith pierces the gap to perfection! Tosses it up, just outside off. Smith advances down the track and caresses it through the extra cover region to bag a boundary.
Fuller and outside off. Smith pushes it towards long off and rotates the strike.
Around off, blocked out.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Cameron Green keeps it out.
FOUR! Punished by Green! A length ball, drifting onto the pads. Green rocks back and whips it through the mid-wicket region. The ball races away to the fence.
Floated, full and outside off. Cameron Green leaves it alone for the keeper to collect.
Tosses it up, around off. Steven Smith gets forward and defends it.
This is around middle and leg. Smith wrists it towards square leg.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Smith tucks it towards square leg but not in the gap.
A bit quicker through the air, on middle. Steven Smith stays back and works it to deep square leg for a single.
A tad short, on middle. Green punches it down to long on for a run.
Khan serves a flighted delivery, on a length, around off. Steven Smith lunges forward and defends it.
Flatter ball, around off. Cameron Green hangs back and defends it.
Floated, full and outside off. Cameron Green prods and pushes it towards extra cover.
Tossed up, outside off. Cameron Green lunges and drives it to the man at extra cover.
A loopy ball, outside off. Cameron Green leans and pushes it to cover.
Floated, on a length, outside off. Cameron Green drives but finds the extra cover fielder yet again.
A bit quicker through the air, on middle. Green stays back and dabs it onto the deck.
Fuller and on middle. Smith defends it back to the bowler.
This is darted on the pads. Steven Smith rocks back and turns it to square leg.
Floated, full and outside off. Steven Smith looks for a booming drive but it goes off the inner half of the bat towards long off for a single.
Around off, blocked out.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Cameron Green hangs back to block it.
A loopy ball, on a length, on off. Cameron Green skips down the track, smothers the spin and pushes it back to the bowler.
Flatter ball, outside off. Steven Smith leaves it alone.
Tosses it up, around off. Steven Smith gets forward and defends it.
This is bowled well wide, outside off. Steven Smith does not bother playing at that one.
Tosses it up, outside off. Steven Smith drives it down to long off for a single.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Cameron Green covers the line and keeps it out.
BEATEN! TURN AND BOUNCE! Ali tosses it up nicely, just outside off. Cameron Green looks to block off the back foot but the ball spins past his outside edge. Terrific delivery to end the over.
A loopy ball, on middle. Steven Smith defends off the front foot.
This is a flatter ball, on middle. Smith keeps it out with ease.
A length ball, drifting onto the pads. Smith tucks it around the corner for a single.
Floated, full and outside off. Green prods and pushes it towards mid off.
A quicker ball, going on with the arm from middle. Cameron Green rocks back and dabs it onto the deck watchfully.
On a length, around middle. Green gets deep in his crease and eases it to long on for a run.
Slightly short and outside off. Green stays back and punches it towards extra cover.
A quicker ball, around off. Cameron Green gets behind the line and defends it.
Ali bowls it slower through the air, full and on off. Cameron Green gets forward and keeps it out.
Floated, on a length, around off. Green covers the line and gets solid in his defence.
Slower through the air, fuller and on off. Green defends it off the front foot.
Fuller in length, on off. Cameron Green gets forward and drives it to the man at extra cover. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 4!
Full and outside off. Steven Smith drives but straight to the cover fielder.
Good-length delivery, around off. Steven Smith hangs back to block it.
Pitches it up, around off. Smith defends it off the front foot.
Another ball, full and outside off. Steven Smith drives it to the fielder at extra cover. No run there!
Shaheen persists with full-length stuff, outside off. Steven Smith sits back and pushes it towards mid off.
A full ball, around off. Steven Smith stays back and eases it to mid off.
Tosses it up, around off. Cameron Green keeps it out off the front foot.
Fuller in length, outside off. Cameron Green skips down and works it to long off. The batters cross ends.
Flatter ball, on a length, outside off. Steven Smith hangs back and punches it to extra cover.
Smith skips down early so Nauman serves it wider, outside off. Steven Smith gets to the pitch of the ball and defends it to the off side.
Floated, around off. Steven Smith gets back and blocks it out.
Looped up, on a length, around off. Steven Smith covers the line of the ball to block it.
Shaheen serves a full ball, around off. Cameron Green gets forward to defend.
Short of a length, around leg. Cameron Green swivels and tucks it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Steven Smith stays back and defends it towards mid on.
A yorker-length ball, on off. Steven Smith digs it out back to the bowler.

Edged but safe! A full ball, angling in from outside off. Smith looks to push it through the off side but it goes off the outside edge which lands in front of the first slip fielder. Abdullah Shafique there, fumbles and the batters take a run.
Shaheen goes for a yorker but ends up serving a low full toss, on the pads. Green tucks it towards fine leg and retains the strike by collecting a single.
Flatter ball, on a length, around middle. Cameron Green hangs back and eases it to mid on for a quick single.
A loopy ball, outside off. Smith runs down the track and drags it wide of mid on for another quick run.

FOUR! Overcooked from Nauman Ali and Green pounces on it! A full ball, outside off. Green gets to the pitch of it and smacks it through the extra cover region. Shaheen Afridi at long off runs to his left, puts in a dive to stop the ball but he fails to do so.
Around off, blocked out.
FOUR! CRUNCHED! Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Green gets on top of the bounce and slaps it through cover for another boundary.
On a length, outside off. Cameron Green punches it to long off for a run.
A short ball, around off. Cameron Green ducks underneath.
Good-length ball, on off. Cameron Green dabs it onto the deck.
Another bumper, angling down leg. Cameron Green does not bother playing at that one.
Short of a length, outside off. Cameron Green stays back and punches it through the cover region for a brace.
Shaheen bends his back and serves another short ball, on middle. Cameron Green ducks underneath.
FOUR! Shaheen looks to surprise Green with a yorker but he ends up bowling a low full toss, around off. Green drills it back past the bowler. The ball races away to the long off fence.
Tosses it up, outside off. Steven Smith gets forward and pushes it back to the bowler.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Steven Smith hangs back and eases it to long on for one run.
Looped up, on a length, around middle. Cameron Green skips down the track and works it to long on for a single.
This is a flatter ball, around middle. Smith stays back and works it to long on. A single taken.
Khan comes 'round the wicket and serves a length ball, on middle. Green stays back to defend it.
On a length, around middle. Cameron Green hangs back and dabs it onto the deck.
A short ball, outside off. Smith shuffles across and pulls it along the ground towards deep square leg for a run.
A bumper, outside off. Cameron Green ducks underneath.
Afridi changes his angle and comes over the wicket now. He serves a back-of-a-length ball, around off. Green hangs back and defends it onto the deck.
Shaheen goes short again, around middle. Cameron Green lets it through to the keeper.
A length ball, around leg. Cameron Green misses his flick and the ball brushes his thigh pad before going to the left of Rizwan behind the sticks.
Banged into the deck, around middle. Cameron Green ducks underneath.
Floated, around middle. Steven Smith stays back to block it.
Floated, on a length, outside off and spinning in. Steven Smith gets low and cuts it past the point fielder for a couple of runs.
Tosses it up, around off. Steven Smith blocks it out.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Steven Smith prods and pushes it to cover.
A bit quicker through the air, on a length, on middle. Steven Smith keeps it out.
Flighted delivery, around middle. Smith sits back and tucks it to mid-wicket.
Finds the gap! Imam starts off with a loosener, a half tracker on middle, this is whipped through mid-wicket for two.
Flatter and on off, Green goes back and defends.
Hiw did he just play that off the back foot? That was quite full and on middle. Green stays back and keeps it out. He got his bat down in time.
Two again! Really good running! On middle, this is worked through mid-wicket. They take the first one quickly and complete the second too.
Lands it nicely. Gives it flight and boles it on off. This is pushed down to long off for one.
A single to end! On middle, this is worked down to long on.

On middle, Smith works it toward square leg. He calls for one, Green takes off but Smith sends him back in time. Smith was almost caught off guard there, he did not expect a throw at his end but it did come at his end. He though makes it back.
On middle, this is pushed back to the bowler.
On the pads, Smith works it fine on the leg side for one.
Flatter and on middle, defended.
Some aggression from the bowler. On middle, this is played back to him. He fires it back at the keeper after collecting it.
Close. Green had to get bat on that. He works this right off the stumps through mid-wicket for one.
Flatter and on middle, this is played to the right of the bowler.
On middle, Green eases it down to long on and takes one. 400 comes up for Australia!
Close! Smith plays for the leg spinner, this is the one that goes on with the arm. It goes off the inner half through square leg for one.
Flatter and on middle, blocked.
Fuller and on off, this is eased down to long off for one.
Gives it air again and lands it on off, it is pushed to covers.
Green comes down the track, does not quite get to the pitch of it. He works it back to the bowler.
Flatter and on middle, defended.
Again uses his feet nicely and eases it down to long off for one.
This lands outside off and turns back in. It is worked to mid-wicket.
On middle, defended.
Another dot to end! On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, around leg. Green flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up, around middle. Smith prods and nudges it to the leg side.
Floated, full and down leg. Smith sweeps it fine but there is a fielder at leg gully who stops it.
Full and on middle. Steven Smith sweeps it to deep mid-wicket and takes a run.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Cameron Green keeps it out.
Floated, full and around leg. Green skips down and digs it out on the leg side.
Flighted ball, on a length, around off. Steven Smith shimmies down and tucks it to square leg.
Tossed up, outside off. Steven Smith skips down and pushes it to mid off.
Around off, blocked out.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Smith defends it off the front foot.
Floated, full and on middle. Smith eases it down to long on and rotates the strike.
An overpitched ball, on middle. Cameron Green nudges it to mid-wicket.
A full ball, down leg. Steven Smith kneels and sweeps it behind square on the leg side for a run.
Darted on the pads. Cameron Green stays back and tucks it to square leg.
Full and around leg. Cameron Green prods and pushes it to mid-wicket.

OUT! CAUGHT! A wicket against the run of play! Green has just thrown away his wicket as he could have hit this loose ball anywhere on the leg side. He would be gutted as he has also fallen just two runs short of his fifty. Nauman Ali serves a half-tracker, down leg. Green gets low and looks to whack it behind square on the leg side. He only manages to get a top edge which lobs up in the air towards the short fine leg fielder who was kept too fine intentionally. Iftikhar Ahmed there, makes no mistake and this is a much-needed breakthrough for Pakistan!
Howout: c Iftikhar Ahmed b Nauman Ali

Commentary: Flatter and on middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
The reverse sweep comes out. It is played through point for one. This is what you'll get with Carey, he's a busy player so if he stays out for sometime, you will probably see Australia score quickly.
Tossed up, on middle. Carey wrists it towards the short leg fielder.
Flatter ball, on middle. Alex Carey keeps it out.
Floated, full and on off. Alex Carey blocks it off the front foot.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Alex Carey pushes it to covers off the back foot.
Slower through the air, on middle, Carey blocks if off the front foot.
A bit quicker, on a length, around middle. Alex Carey keeps it out.
TURN AND BOUNCE! A flatter ball, on leg and spinning away from the batter. Smith looks to defend off the back foot but he misses and gets hit high on his body.
A full ball, on middle. Steven Smith flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Floated, full and on off. Alex Carey prods and just paddles it towards short fine leg. Not in the gap though!
Tossed up, around off. Alex Carey gets forward and blocks it.
FOUR! Nails his reverse sweep this time! Tossed up, outside off. Alex Carey kneels and reverse sweeps it behind square on the off side for a boundary.

FOUR! Just over the slip fielder! Another ball, tossed up, outside off. Alex Carey gets down on his knee to reverse sweep yet again. He does not middle it this time as it goes off the top edge. Babar Azam at first slip hops to grab the ball but it goes over him and into the fence for another boundary.
Flatter and on off. Blocked out.
A loopy ball, on middle. Smith tucks it to the leg side.
Floated, around middle. Smith keeps it out.
Darted on the pads. Steven Smith prods and works it to square leg.
Slower through the air, on a length, around off. Smith gets forward to block it.
FOUR! Top shot! Khan serves a flighted delivery, well outside off. Smith reaches out and carves it past the mid off fielder to bag a boundary.
Floated, full and on middle. Alex Carey digs it out to mid-wicket.
Looped up, full and outside off. Alex Carey gets forward and reverse sweeps it to deep point. A single taken!
Nauman serves a flighted ball, down leg. Steven Smith looks for a reverse sweep but he fails to get any bat on it.
Another ball, down leg. Steven Smith looks to whack it through fine leg but he misses.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! So the ploy to bowl from over the wicket and around Smith's pads has done wonders for Pakistan! Another Australian batter who gifts his wicket away! Nauman Ali serves a flatter ball, down leg. Smith prods and tries to sweep it fine through the fine leg region but he fails to do so. The ball brushes off his glove and goes to Mohammad Rizwan behind the sticks who takes a sharp catch. Pakistan are ecstatic as they should be! Another Aussie batter fails to go on and get a big one after getting set. Australia lose their sixth wicket now!
Howout: c Mohammad Rizwan b Nauman Ali

Commentary: Flatter and outside off, this stays low. Starc looks to push but it goes off the underedge and on the bounce to the first slip fielder.
Flatter and on off, defended.
Fires it on middle again, Carey easily keeps it out.
Tosses it up on middle, Carey keeps it out.
Loopy ball on middle, blocked.
Slightly fuller and on off, this is pushed to covers.
On middle, Carey leans forward and defends. A maiden by Khan.
Flatter ball, on a length, outside off. Mitchell Starc pushes it through covers and takes a single to get off the mark.
Carey plays another reverse sweep towards deep point and rotates the strike.
Floated, around middle. Mitchell Starc keeps it out.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Starc prods and defends it.
Tossed up, outside off. Mitchell Starc gets forward and pushes it back to the bowler.
This is darted on the pads. Starc flicks it through square leg and collects a run.
Tossed up, on middle. Mitchell Starc stays back and pushes it towards mid on.
An overpitched ball, on middle. Starc digs it out.
Slower through the air, on a length, around middle. Mitchell Starc gets forward and blocks it.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Mitchell Starc rocks back and punches it to the man at cover-point.
Floated, on a length, around off. Starc looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards the first slip fielder, on the bounce.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Mitchell Starc dabs it onto the deck.
Looped up, full and outside off. Carey gets down on his knee and sweeps it to deep square leg for one run.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Mitchell Starc pushes it back to the bowler.
Floated, on a length, around off. Starc lunges forward and keeps it out.
A full ball, outside off. Mitchell Starc prods and drives it to cover. Not in the gap though!
Tossed up, around off. Mitchell Starc leans and defends it onto the deck.
A wayward delivery, down leg. Mitchell Starc stays back and leaves it alone.
Flighted ball, around off. Carey blocks it solidly.
Flatter and quicker, on off. Alex Carey rocks back and punches it to mid off.

FOUR! Excellent timing and even better from placement from Carey! A half-volley, outside off. Carey gets to the pitch of delivery and carves it past Shaheen Afridi at mid off to fetch himself a boundary. Lovely shot!
Tossed up, on off. Alex Carey keeps it out.
Tossed up, on middle. Alex Carey gets forward and defends.
A yorker-length ball, on middle. Alex Carey digs it out watchfully.

NOT OUT! This was a yorker, around leg. Mitchell Starc fails to dig it out and gets hit low on his pad. Shaheen Afridi sppeals but the umpire says no. Babar Azam opts for a review and the Ball Tracker shows that the ball would have gone down leg. Starc survives.
Back of a length, down leg. Mitchell Starc leaves it alone.
On a length, around middle. Mitchell Starc nudges it through mid-wicket and takes a couple of runs.
Another full ball, angling in from middle. Mitchell Starc jams it out watchfully.
A well-directed bumper, around off. Starc stays back and looks to block but he gets hit high on his bat.
A pinpoint yorker, around off. Mitchell Starc digs it out back to the bowler.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Alex Carey stays back and works it towards point.
Tossed up, around off. Alex Carey gets forward to block it.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Carey punches it towards cover.
Tossed up, outside off. Alex Carey leans and pushes it towards mid off.
Floated, on a length, around off. Alex Carey lunges forward and keeps it out.
On a length, around middle. Carey blocks it off the front foot.
Fuller and outside off, left alone.
Angling into the middle pole, Starc works it to mid on.
Good length and on off, this is pushed to covers.
Short and on the body, Starc fends it away on the leg side.
Digs it short again and on the body, once again it comes at an uncomfortable height for Starc. He manages to nudge it down to fine leg for one.
Fuller and on off, this is pushed to mid off.
A full ball, angling down leg. Mitchell Starc misses his flick and Mohammad Rizwan does well behind the sticks to dive to his right to stop the ball.
Good-length ball, around middle. Mitchell Starc nudges it around the corner and takes a single.
This is full and on middle. Alex Carey prods and pushes it towards mid on.
Back of a length, around off. Alex Carey hangs back and dabs it onto the deck.
Full and well outside off. Alex Carey lets it sail through to the keeper.
A low full toss, around the pads. Alex Carey tickles it to fine leg and retains the strike by taking a single.
A bumper, around middle. Alex Carey ducks underneath.
Bye! A full ball, angling down leg. Alex Carey misses his flick and Rizwan fails to grab it cleanly. The ball rolls away towards fine leg and they take a bye.
Back of a length, nipping down leg. Mitchell Starc hops in his crease to flick but fails to get any bat on it.
Short of a length, around off. Mitchell Starc hangs back to defend it to the off side.
A yorker, just missing leg. Mitchell Starc does not get any blade on it.
Back of a length, just outside off. Starc gets on top of the bounce and taps it to the off side for a quick single.
FOUR! EDGY! Banged into the deck, around off. Starc stays back to defend but it goes off the outside edge past the first slip fielder and races away to the fence.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Mitchell Starc keeps it out.

Bye! A full ball, angling down leg. Starc misses his nudge on the leg side and Rizwan behind the sticks half-stops it. The batters take a bye. Rizwan seems to have hurt his right hand yet again and looks in pain.
This is full and outside off. Alex Carey drives it wide of the mid off fielder and takes a couple of runs.

OUT! TIMBER! Naseem Shah strikes and this is a peach of a delivery by the youngster to get rid of Carey! Shah comes 'round the wicket and serves a length ball, just outside off. The ball nips back in slightly and Carey plays it down the wrong line as he tries to block it. The ball hits the top of off stump and Carey is a goner. Pakistan on top at the moment as Australia lose their seventh wicket now. Pat Cummins walks out to bat.
Short of a length, around off. Cummins blocks it out.
Tossed up, outside off. Mitchell Starc drives it through cover and takes a single.
FOUR! CRUNCHED! Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Pat Cummins rocks back and cuts it past point to bag a boundary.
Around off, blocked out.
Flatter ball, around off. Cummins defends it off the back foot.
Floated, well outside off. Pat Cummins leaves it alone.
Tossed up, around off. Pat Cummins keeps it out.

Some movement straightaway for Shaheen! A length ball, nipping back in from middle. Mitchell Starc stays back to block but he misses and gets rapped on his pad. Shaheen appeals but the umpire, Aleem Dar is unmoved.
Back of a length, outside off. Mitchell Starc leaves it alone.
A length ball, angling down leg. Mitchell Starc fails to get any bat on it as he tries to flick it.
Leg bye! A full ball, angling in from middle. Starc looks to flick but he misses and gets hit low on his pad. The ball rolls to the leg side for a leg bye.
FOUR! Nicely played! 450 comes up for Australia! A full ball, on middle. Cummins stays back, opens the bat face and steers it past the backward point fielder to bag a boundary.

Leg bye! Afridi comes 'round the wicket and serves a full ball, around leg. Pat Cummins misses his nudge on the leg side and the ball brushes off his pad before going to the keeper. Rizwan half-stops it with a dive and the batters take a leg bye.
Tosses it up, around off. Pat Cummins gets forward to block it.
Looped up, on a length, around off. Pat Cummins defends it off the front foot.

OUT! CAUGHT! A soft dismissal and Nauman Ali bags a five-wicket haul! He tosses it up nicely, outside off, enticing the batter to drive. Cummins prods and looks to drive it away from his body through cover. It goes off the outer half of the blade and he just chips it in the end towards Imam-ul-Haq at extra cover who takes a sharp catch. Pat Cummins stands there in disbelief. Pakistan strike early on Day 5!
Tossed up, around off. Lyon blocks it off the front foot.
BEATEN! This is tossed up, outside off. The ball spins past Lyon's outside edge as he tries to defend it off the front foot.
Fuller and on off. Lyon gets forward and keeps it out. A wicket-maiden from Nauman Ali. Superb bowling!
A full ball, outside off. Mitchell Starc digs it out back to the bowler.
A short ball, around leg. Mitchell Starc miscues his pull towards square leg and takes a single.
A length ball, angling in from middle. Nathan Lyon misses his flick shot and gets hit high on his pad.
A full ball, angling in from middle. Lyon prods and flicks it past the mid on fielder to take a couple of runs.
Another ball, full and on middle. Lyon flicks but this time Nauman Ali at mid on dives to his right and half-stops it. Just the single.

OUT! LBW! That looked plumb in front! Shaheen Afridi doing what he does best! He runs in and serves a yorker, angling in from off. Mitchell Starc fails to dig it out and gets hit low on his pad. Shaheen Afridi appeals and the umpire agrees. Starc opts for a review straightaway! No bat involved, confirms the UltraEdge. The Ball Tracker rolls in and it indicates three reds. Pakistan have their ninth wicket.

OUT! LBW! Nauman Ali picks his sixth wicket and that is it for Australia! Nauman Ali serves a flatter ball, on off that goes on with the arm. Nathan Lyon kneels and looks to sweep but he misses and gets pinged on his pad. Ali appeals and the umpire raises his finger. Lyon though takes a review but to no avail. The Ball Tracker indicates three reds and it is plumb. Lyon, however, had already taken the walk back to the pavilion. Australia are bowled out for 459.
Back of a length, down leg. Abdullah Shafique tries to flick but he misses. A stifled appeal for caught behind but the umpire is unmoved.
On a length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique leaves it alone.
Full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique lets it through to the keeper.
This is a length ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique prods and keeps it out.
Fuller in length, around middle. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and defends it awkwardly towards mid-wicket.
Good-length ball, well outside off. Abdullah Shafique does not bother playing at that one.
On a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it off the front foot.
Pitches it up, around off. Imam-ul-Haq gets forward and defends it.
Back of a length, just outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
Another ball, full and around middle. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.
Hazlewood serves a full ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq flicks it past the mid-wicket fielder and gets off the mark with a single.
Pitches it up, just outside off. Abdullah Shafique looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards the slip fielder, along the ground.
Back of a length, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq stays back to block.
This is darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq tucks it towards deep square leg and takes a single.
Starc goes full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique slices it towards deep point for one run. Both the openers are up and running now!

An overthrow and they get five runs! Good-length ball, around off. Imam-ul-Haq taps it towards cover and takes off for a single. Usman Khawaja runs in from cover and misses his shy at the bowler's end. There is no one backing up and the ball races away to the fence. Sloppy from Australia!
Back of a length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique leaves it alone.
Slightly shorter in length, well outside off. Abdullah Shafique lets it through to the keeper.
Good-length ball, around off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it off the front foot.
On a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq leans and keeps it out on the off side.
A length ball, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it around the corner and takes a run.
Good-length ball, nipping back in from middle. Abdullah Shafique misses his nudge on the leg side and gets hit high on his pad.
Pitched up, around off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and keeps it out.
A full ball, angling in from middle. Abdullah Shafique flicks but Nathan Lyon at mid-wicket, dives to his left and stops the ball.
Good-length ball, way down leg. Imam-ul-Haq does not bother playing at it.
A length ball, around middle and leg. Imam-ul-Haq tickles it to fine leg and hands the strike back to Abdullah Shafique.
Back of a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique sits back in his crease and dabs it onto the deck.
Another ball, short and around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
FOUR! CUT AWAY! Width on offer and Abdullah Shafique pounces on it. Short of a length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique slaps it past the point fielder and bags a boundary.
Starc goes full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique leans and drives it wide of deep cover for a couple of runs.

FOUR! EDGY! Turn straightaway for Lyon! This is a flatter ball, around off and spinning away from the left-hander. Imam-ul-Haq stays back to block but it goes off the outside edge past the first slip fielder and into the third man fence.
Tosses it up, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq skips down and pushes it to cover.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq punches it to sweeper cover for a single.
Floated, full and on off. Abdullah Shafique prods and defends it.
That stayed a bit low! A loopy ball, outside off and turning in late. Abdullah Shafique stays back to defend but the ball keeps a bit low and gets the toe end of his bat.
Tosses it up, around off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.
Back of a length, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq stays back and blocks it out.

FOUR! Aerial but Imam-ul-Haq is lucky to escape! This is a well-directed short ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq looks to pull but the ball hurries onto him and he mistimes it in the air wide of the deep square leg fielder. The ball falls just wide of Nathan Lyon at deep square leg who dives to his left. Two bounces and into the ropes.
On a length, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq lets it be.
FOUR! Nicely timed! A full ball, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq flicks it behind square on the leg side and bags another boundary.
Another short ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq ducks underneath.
Short of a length, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq hangs back to defend it.
Tosses it up, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Sharp turn! Tossed up, on a length, well outside off. Abdullah Shafique looks to play it across the line but he misses as the ball sneaks through his bat and pad.
Floated, on middle. Abdullah Shafique tucks it to the leg side for a single.
This is darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq rocks back and nudges it towards square leg.
Tosses it up, on off. Imam-ul-Haq gets solid in his front foot defence.
A bit quicker through the air from Lyon, around off. Imam-ul-Haq gets back in his crease to block it.
FOUR! Easy pickings! Cummins starts with a loosener, a length ball, around leg. Abdullah Shafique glances it through fine leg and collects a boundary.

NO BALL AND FOUR! Cummins errs in line again! Another ball, drifting onto the pads. Abdullah Shafique tickles it through fine leg and fetches another boundary. Pat Cummins oversteps and the umpire signals a no ball.
BEAUTY! Good-length ball, just outside off that shapes away a bit. Abdullah Shafique looks to defend but the ball zips past his outside edge. Good comeback from the Aussie skipper.
On a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it out.
A full ball, around leg. Abdullah Shafique tickles it to fine leg and takes a single this time.
Edged but safe! A length ball, around off and angling across the left-hander. Imam-ul-Haq tries to block but it goes off outside edge and goes to the gully fielder, on the bounce.
A short ball, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq ducks underneath.
Tossed up on off, turning in. Defended.
FOUR! Pakistan are scoring quickly here! Short and wide outside off, Abdullah Shafique goes back and pushes it through covers and this one races away to the fence.
Floats it up on middle, Abdullah Shafique leans forward and keeps it out.
Another one nicely flighted and on off, blocked.
Floats it up on off, kept out.
Another forward defensive stroke to this ball on off.
Good-length ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.
This is angling down leg. Imam-ul-Haq misses his flick and the ball brushes off his pad before going to Alex Carey behind the sticks.
Short of a length, nipping back into the batter. Imam-ul-Haq misses his nudge on the leg side.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Imam-ul-Haq tucks it behind square on the leg side and takes a single.
A short ball, around off. Abdullah Shafique stays back and dabs it onto the deck with soft hands.
BEATEN! A length ball, around the corridor of uncertainty. Abdullah Shafique looks to defend but the ball zips past his outside edge. Lovely bowling from the Aussie skipper.
Tosses it up, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq skips down the track and pushes it to mid on.
SIX! Nails his shot this time! Imam-ul-Haq advances down the track to this length ball and lofts it back over the bowler's head to fetch a maximum.
Floated, full and outside off. Imam-ul-Haq drives it down to long off for one run.
Around off, blocked out.
Tosses it up, outside off. Abdullah Shafique skips down the track, smothers the spin and eases it to long on for a single.
Flatter and quicker, on a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.
A full ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique looks to flick and the ball takes the outside edge. Luckily for Abdullah Shafique, the ball falls short of the slip fielder.
Fuller in length, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets on top of the bounce and dabs it onto the deck.
A short ball, angling in from outside off. Abdullah Shafique sways away from the line of the ball.
A full ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique tries to defend but it goes off the thick inside edge towards fine leg for a run.
Back of a length, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq prods to defend but it takes the outside edge which rolls towards the gully fielder.
Tossed up, well outside off. Abdullah Shafique smothers the spin and eases it to long on for a run.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq slaps it through cover and takes a single.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets to the pitch of the ball and blocks it.

Shouts of catch it but the ball falls short of Lyon! A bit short, outside off and spinning in late. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and chips it back to the bowler uppishly. The ball bounces just in front of Lyon who tries to grab it.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Tosses it up nicely, well outside off. Abdullah Shafique stretches forward and blocks it.

Just over! Leg bye signaled though so would not have mattered if it had gone to hand. Short and on the body, Imam looks to evade it, it hits him on the forearm, then the chest and goes over Carey and down to fine leg for a leg bye. He is in pain now.
That is very well played! Short and on middle, Abdullah Shafique, with one leg up in the air, pulls it through mid-wicket for one. They should have ran better, there was a chance of two there.
Good length now and on off, Imam hangs back and defends.
Angled into the pads, Imam works it through square leg for one.
On off, defended.
Goes short and on middle, this is pulled through square leg for one. Cracking shot just for one.

FOUR! How has that missed the off pole? What a delivery! This lands outside off, well outside off and turns back in. Abdullah Shafique lunges and looks to defend, it takes the inside edge and just about kisses the off pole, it goes very close past it and down to the fine leg fence.
Tossed up on off, blocked.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Another one floated up on off, defended.
Nicely tosses it up and on off, Shafique works it to mid-wicket.

Lands it around off, Abdullah Shafique comes forward and blocks. A really good over from Nathan Lyon! Unlike the first innings, he is bowling it outside off and getting it to turn back in. That is where he becomes very dangerous, that turn and the bounce he gets is what causes the batters problems.
Lands it well, on off, Imam works it to mid-wicket.
Skips down the track now and eases it down to long on for one.
Lands it well again, floats it up on off, this is pushed back to the bowler.
Outside off, left alone.

NOT OUT! The impact is well outside off. Always seemed that way. Australia lose a review. This is given a nice loop. It lands on off. Abdullah Shafique looks to play the paddle sweep but the ball dips at the very end, sneaks under the bat and hits the pad. A huge shout but turned down. It is reviewed. Replays show that the on-field call is the right one.
Angled into the pads, Imam works it to square leg.
Flatter and on middle, defended.
On middle, it is worked to mid-wicket.
On the stumps, defended.
Another one tossed up on off, Abdullah Shafique pushes it to mid off.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Floats it up on off, Abdullah Shafique defends.
Another loopy delivery on off, blocked.
Flighted and on off, Imam pushes it to covers.
Fuller and on off, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Shorter and on middle, Imam works it through square leg for one.
Shorter and outside off, Abdullah Shafique looks to cut but underedges it on the off side.
Floats it up on off, Abdullah Shafique pushes it to covers.
Outside off, left alone.
Another one tossed up and bowled well outside off, not played at.
Yet again this one is well outside off, Imam shoulders arms to this one.
Gives it air and lands it outside off, it is driven to covers.
Outside off, shortish. Imam rocks back and cuts it through point for one.
A single to end as this is worked with the spin through square leg.
Flighted and on off, defended.
On middle, this is worked to mid on for one.
Gives it air and lands it on off, it is flicked to mid-wicket.
Fuller and outside off, Imam pushes it to covers.
Tossed up on off, defended.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
This lands outside off and turns back in, it is worked to mid-wicket.
On middle, blocked.
On the stumps, kept out.
On off, this stays a touch low. Abdullah Shafique defends.
Flatter and on off, Abdullah Shafique pushes it to mid on.
Yet another tidy over! On the stumps, blocked.
On the stumps Imam defends it out.
On off, this is pushed to mid on.
A single as this is worked through mid-wicket.
Slightly shorter again, Abdullah Shafique pulls it through mid-wicket and gets to the other end.
FOUR! That is a lovely shot! Uses his feet and makes it into a full toss, it is driven through covers for a boundary.
Marnus Labuschagne continues to toss it up, lands it on off, it is worked to mid on. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 5!
Flatter ball, around middle and turning in late. Abdullah Shafique stays back and wrists it behind square on the leg side.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.
This is darted on the pads. Abdullah Shafique hangs back and tucks it to short fine leg.
On a length, around middle and turning in late. Abdullah Shafique waits for the turn and then glances it to the man at short fine leg.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Abdullah Shafique nudges it to mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, around off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot. A maiden over from Nathan Lyon!
Starc starts with a full ball, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq prods and eases it to mid-wicket.
Good-length delivery, around off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it off the back foot.
A full ball, angling in from middle. Imam-ul-Haq gets forward and pushes it to mid on.
Fuller in length, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq tickles it to fine leg and collects a single.
Back of a length, around middle. Abdullah Shafique covers the line and defends it to the on side.
Starc pitches it up, around off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and blocks it solidly.
Tossed up, very full and on off, it is jammed out to covers.
Shorter and outside off, Imam cuts it through point and takes two.
Goes short again, this is also cut through point for one.
On off, this is pushed to covers.
This lands outside off and turns back in. Abdullah Shafique looks to defend but it goes off the inner half on the leg side.
On off, blocked.
Some inward movement for Starc! It is on middle, Imam clips it to mid-wicket.
Good length and on off, Imam shows the full face of the bat and plays it back to the bowler.
On the stumps, Imam shows the full face of the bat and plays it to mid off.
Outside off, left alone.
Outside off, Imam opens the face of the bat and guides it down to third man for one.
Length and on off, this one also shapes away. Abdullah Shafique looks to defend, it goes off the outer half through point for one.
On off, blocked.
Tossed up on off again, kept out.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Well played in the end! Abdullah Shafique gets down the wicket, he does not get to the pitch of the ball but puts in a good stride forward and hits it against the turn through covers for two.
Now takes one as he works it through square leg.
Outside off, left alone.
Well fielded! Outside off, this is guided through backward point. Lyon runs to his left, slides and makes a good stop.

Edged but safe! Good fielding by Lyon again! Outside off, shaping away. Abdullah Shafique goes after it, it flies off the outside edge wide of the diving gully fielder. Lyon runs to his left from deep point, dives and saves two again for his side.
Good length and on off, defended.
Down the leg side, left alone.
Good shot but for no runs! Length and on off, it is driven nicely but to covers.
Outside off, not played at.
Slower and outside off, left alone.
On off, this is pushed to covers.
Floats it up on off, Imam defends.
Well wide outside off again, left alone.
Another one which is quite wide outside off, not played at.
Slightly shorter in length and outside off, it is cut but to point.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed to mid on for one.
Outside off, left alone.
Good length and on middle, kept out.
Another one on the stumps, blocked.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Outside off, not played at.
Another run as this is pushed down to long on.
Steps out now, this is bowled from around the wicket, outside leg, it is worked to mid on.
Shorter and on the pads, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Now Lyon is bowling the down the leg side line. He was bowling outside off before this to Imam. Imam though lets it go.
Flatter and on off, defended.
On the pads, this is worked to square leg.
Fuller and shaping back in, Abdullah Shafique works it through mid-wicket and takes one.
Outside off, this is guided through point for one.
On off, this is pushed through covers for one.
On off, defended.
On middle, Shafique keeps it out.
Length again and on off, Shafique keeps it out.
Lyon comes over the wicket and serves a length ball, on leg. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.
Tossed up, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq skips down the track and blocks it onto the deck.
Flatter and on middle. Imam wrists it towards short leg.
Tosses it up, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it.

FOUR! Imam brings up his FIFTY in style! This is floated, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq kneels and reverse sweeps it through the point region to bag a boundary. What a Test match he is having! A hundred in the first innings and now he gets to his fifty in the second innings.
This is darted on the pads. Imam stays back and tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique gets behind the line to block it.
Pitches it up, around middle. Abdullah Shafique prods and defends it towards mid on.
Good-length ball, angling in from middle. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and blocks it solidly.

Had Pat Cummins collected the ball cleanly, Abdullah Shafique might have been in trouble at the bowler's end. A length ball, on middle. Abdullah Shafique taps it to mid on and sets off for a single. Cummins at mid on fails to grab the ball cleanly and Abdullah Shafique gets home safely.
On a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq stays back to block it.
Back of a length, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq tries to cut but it goes off the underedge and onto the deck.
Flatter ball, on middle. Abdullah Shafique wrists it towards the short leg fielder.
FOUR! Width on offer and Abdullah Shafique smashes it hard to bring up his FIFTY! A short ball, outside off. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and cuts it past the point fielder for a boundary.
Tossed up, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and defends it.
Flatter ball, on a length, around middle and turning in late. Abdullah Shafique tucks it to the leg side and takes a run.

Edged but safe! Lyon tosses it up nicely, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq prods to block but it takes the outside edge and goes past Steven Smith at first slip. The fielder at short third man cuts it off and the batters take three runs.
Floated, outside off and turning in late. Imam tucks it to square leg.
Floated, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq stays back and punches it through cover for a run.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique sits back and taps it towards point.
Slower through the air, full and on middle. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.
Tossed up, on off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and keeps it out.
Slightly shorter in length, around middle and leg. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and nudges it to the leg side for a single.
Floated, outside off. Abdullah Shafique stays back and taps it to point.
Fuller and around off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.
Lyon bowls it slower through the air, on middle. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
This is a flighted delivery, on middle. Abdullah Shafique smothers the spin and tucks it to the leg side for a single.
Flatter ball, around off. Imam-ul-Haq hangs back and blocks it out.
Darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq gets back in his crease and turns it towards square leg.
A low ful toss, outside off. Abdullah Shafique prods and drives it to cover-point.
Tossed up, outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and pushes it to cover.
FOUR! Deft touch! Shorter in length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and just guides it past the short third man fielder for a boundary.
Flatter ball, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Abdullah Shafique tucks it to mid-wicket.
An overpitched ball, outside off. Abdullah Shafique prods and works it to mid off. He wanted a single but is sent back by Imam.
This is darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq stays back and nudges it behind square on the leg side for a run.
Flatter ball, on off and spinning in late. Abdullah Shafique stays back and wrists it uppishly just past the short leg fielder for a run.
A length ball, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq rocks back and tickles it towards short fine leg.

EDGED BUT SAFE! This is a flatter ball, landing outside leg and spinning away sharply. Imam-ul-Haq looks to defend off the back foot but it takes the outside edge and goes past Steven Smith at first slip. Lovely bowling from Lyon!
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.

Aerial but safe yet again! Imam-ul-Haq is riding his luck here! He skips down the track and looks to go downtown. It goes off the outer half of the blade and over the mid off fielder for a couple of runs.
Full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique drives it to mid off.
Tossed up, on middle. Abdullah Shafique drives it straight back to the bowler. Marnus Labuschagne gets hit on his ankle. He looks in some pain.
Floated, on middle. Abdullah Shafique blocks it out.
FOUR! Good use of the feet! Floated, on off. Abdullah Shafique skips down the track and drills it back past the bowler. The ball races away to the long off fence.
Slower through the air, full and on off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it to the off side.
On a length, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq prods and tickles it to short fine leg.
Tossed up, on middle. Abdullah Shafique gets on his knee and sweeps it behind square on the leg side for a brace.
Flatter ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique nudges it to short fine leg.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique prods and drives it wide of mid off for a single.
Floated, down leg. Imam lunges forward and tickles it to short fine leg.
Flatter and on middle. Imam rocks back and nudges it to mid-wicket.

SIX! BANG! The Pakistani openers are showing some intent now! Brilliant use of the feet and Imam fetches a biggie. Tossed up, on leg. Imam skips down the track and sends it sailing way over long on. Will they go hard at the Aussies now?
An overpitched ball, on middle. Abdullah Shafique digs it out to the leg side for a run.
FOUR! Pierces the gap to perfection! Tossed up, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq prods and carves it through the cover region to bag a boundary. There were two fielders at cover but he split them nicely.
A wayward ball, well outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq slaps it through cover and settles for a single.
Slower through the air, on a length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out off the front foot.
A loopy ball, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and blocks it.
On the pads, this is worked through square leg for one.
Flatter and on middle, Abdullah Shafique defends it.
FOUR! Very nicely played! The paddle scoop, he actually drags this from well outside off. It was a pre-meditated shot. Comes off and Abdullah Shafique bags a boundary.
Flatter and on off, Abdullah Shafique defends it onto the ground.
Sent back in time! Abdullah Shafique steps out and pushes it to mid off. He is off for a run but Imam sends him back, just in time.
A single to end! On middle, this is worked through square leg for one.
On middle, this is worked to mid on.
A single this time as mid on is pushed back to long on and it is played to that fielder.
Fuller and outside off, Imam drives but to covers.
Outside off again, this is not played at.
Outside off, left alone again.
Three leaves in a row as this is also bowled outside off.
Imam saves a few runs there for Australia! On middle, this is hit hard towards the non-striker who fails to get out of the way in time and the ball hits him.
FOUR! Up and over! That is a hit-me ball! From around the wicket, Marnus bowls it short and on middle, this is pulled over the mid-wicket fielder for a boundary. 150 up.
Now lands it right, on middle, AS defends.

Close! Marnus Labuschagne almost does a Shane Warne! This is bowled outside leg, on the rough. Abdullah Shafique looks to sweep but misses. It just goes past the leg pole. We have seen the great man Shane Warne do it a lot of times during his playing days. Marnus Labuschagne did come close there.
On the pads, this is worked to mid-wicket.
On middle, this is pushed to mid on.
Fuller and on off, this is hit down to long off for one.

What just happened there? Surprisingly, Australia did not appeal or maybe they just wanted to keep the spirit of the game alive. This is on off, Abdullah Shafique looks to defend, it lands in front of him and then seems like rolling back towards the stumps. He bends down and picks the ball up. Carey and Smith have a puzzled look on their face but the ball is tossed back to the bowler and on we go again.
A single as this is pushed down to long on.
Imam looks to aggressive. Steps out, this is bowled outside off. He slashes, it goes more off the outer half through point for two.
Outside off, left alone.
On middle, defended.
On middle, kept out.
A single as this is worked through mid-wicket.
Another one as Imam eases it to long on.
Shorter and on the pads, this is flicked through mid-wicket for one.
Steps out and gets close to the pitch of the ball, it is pushed to covers.

A direct hit would have been very close! Maybe out! That was a rocket through from the fielder. On middle, this is worked to mid on. Abdullah Shafique is just jogging towards the other end, he then realises the throw is at his end and then puts in the hard yards. Luckily for him, it is just over the stumps.
On off, Imam pushes it to covers for one.
Tossed up on middle, this is eased down to long on for one.
Outside off, this lands and spins away a long way. Left alone.
On off, this is pushed to the right of the bowler.
Another one outside off, not played at.
Shorter and outside off, this is cut through point for one.
Shorter and on middle, it is pulled through mid-wicket for one.
On middle, kept out.
Fuller and on middle, this is eased down to long on for one.
Imam steps out and works it down to long on for one.
Another run! Fuller and on middle, this is worked wide of mid on for a single.
Good fielding! This is tossed up on off, Imam hits it wide of mid off. Starc runs there, dives and saves three for his side.
Tossed up on off, blocked.
Outside off, left alone.
Imam steps down the track and hits it hard back towards Head who misfields and a run is taken.
Tossed up on off, this is pushed back to the bowler.
Shafique steps out, does not get to the pitch of it and hence, defends.
Tossed up on off, Abdullah Shafique pushes it through covers and takes three.
Smith serves a shorter length delivery, down leg. Abdullah Shafique hangs back and whips it through the square leg region for a couple of runs.
Tosses it up, around middle. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.

SIX! BOOM! A half-tracker from Smith, around middle. Abdullah Shafique gets back, shuffles across and whacks it way over the deep mid-wicket fence for a biggie. A gift from Steven Smith! Shafique moves into the 90s now!
Floated, around leg. Abdullah Shafique hangs back and nudges it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq drives but finds the cover fielder.
This is darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq tickles it through fine leg and collects a run.
On off, this is pushed to covers.
Around off, defended.
Well played! Outside off, Imam guides it down to third man for two.
On middle, defended.
Flatter and on off, Imam pushes it to covers.
Two more! Fuller and on middle, this is hit down towards long on for two.
Tossed up on off, defended.
On off, this is pushed to cover. AS wants a run but is sent back.
That has stayed low! Outside off, this does not bounce a lot. Abdullah Shafique somehow pushes it to covers.
Shorter and on middle, this is pulled through square leg for one.
FOUR! Up and over! Safe shot with the fielders in the ring on the leg side. Shorter and on middle, Imam pulls it over mid-wicket for a boundary.
On middle, blocked.
On middle, blocked.
Two more and Abdullah Shafique moves onto 99! On the pads, this is clipped through square leg for two.
Tosses it up, around middle. Abdullah Shafique prods and keeps it out.
Slower through the air, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets forward and blocks it with ease.
Flighted delivery, fuller and wider, outside off. Abdullah Shafique stretches forward to defend this one.
Flatter ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and guides it towards short fine leg. Not in the gap though! THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 5!
Tosses it up, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it off the back foot.
This is a length ball, down leg. Imam stays back and tucks it to square leg.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it to square leg yet again.
Tossed up, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq looks to sweep but he fails to get any bat on it.
Interesting leave from Imam! Flatter and quicker, on a length, around leg and spinning away late. Imam-ul-Haq stays back to leave it but the ball bounces sharply and he gets hit high on his body.
Floated, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq prods and keeps it out.

A length ball, around leg. Abdullah Shafique prods and tickles it to fine leg for a run. CENTURY for Abdullah Shafique! What a fine knock this has been from the youngster! A maiden Test hundred for Shafique and his teammates are delighted for him in the change room.
Full and outside off. Imam-ul-Haq drives it to sweeper cover and takes a single.
On a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.
NO BALL! A short ball, outside off. Abdullah Shafique sways away from the line of the delivery. Cameron Green oversteps and the umpire signals no ball.
Back of a length, around middle. Abdullah Shafique tucks it to square leg.
Good-length delivery, around off. Abdullah Shafique defends it off the front foot.
A length ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique hangs back and nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on off. Imam-ul-Haq plays the reverse sweep through point and takes a couple of runs.
This is tossed up, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq misses his flick.
Darted on the pads. Imam tucks it to square leg.
Flatter ball, on a length, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it around the corner and settles for a single.
Flatter ball, on middle. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Tosses it up, outside off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
A short one to begin the over! Ducked under.

Direct hit and it would have been close! Really good from Marnus Labuschagne! On off, this is pushed towards him at covers. He gets to the ball quickly, turns and has a shy at the bowler's end but misses. Imam did put the dive in but that would not have saved him.
On middle, kept out.
FOUR! Very nicely played! Sheer timing! Shorter and on off, Abdullah Shafique pushes it through covers for a boundary. 200 comes up for Pakistan!
NO BALL! On middle, this is pushed back to the bowler. Cameron Green has overstepped.
Shorter and on middle, this is pushed to covers.
A dot to end! On middle, defended.
Risky! Gets away with it! Imam comes down the track, Lyon bowls it slightly shorter and around leg. Imam swings, it goes off the inside edge towards fine leg. Lucky escape.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.

An appeal but turned down! Lyon was not that interested. Oh no... Ultra Edge shows a spike. Australia have been so poor with the reviews in this game. They missed a couple in the first innings and now one here. This is on the pads. Imam looks to flick, it seems to have gone off the pad to short leg. Both the fielder and the keeper celebrate but the bowler is not interested. A life for Imam-ul-Haq!
On middle, defended.
On middle, this is worked through mid-wicket for one.
On middle, kept out.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed to mid on for one.
Fuller and on middle, this is worked through square leg for one.
Down the leg side, left alone.
On off, kept out.
Fuller and on middle, this is driven down the ground for one.
On middle, blocked.
Flatter ball, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq rocks back and punches it to cover.
This is darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it to the leg side.

NOT OUT! Australia lose another review! This is a flatter ball, down leg. Imam-ul-Haq looks to flick but he misses. Nathan Lyon appeals but the umpire says no! Pat Cummins opts for a review but the UltraEdge shows that there is no bat involved and the on-field decision remains.
Around leg. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it to the leg side for a single.
Tossed up, outside off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it out.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Abdullah Shafique stretches forward and defends it.
Drop and run! Back of a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq taps it towards point and sets off for a quick run. Imam moves to 99 now!
A full ball, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
A length ball, angling down leg. Abdullah Shafique lets it through to the keeper.
On a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique defends it to the off side and takes a quick single.
A short ball, well outside off. Imam-ul-Haq stays back and flat-bats it to extra cover.
A bumper, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq ducks underneath.
Tossed up, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique defends off the front foot.
Slower through the air, on off. Abdullah Shafique gets to the pitch of the ball and dabs it onto the deck.
Fuller in length, on middle. Abdullah Shafique defends it off the front foot.
FOUR! Tosses it up, on off. Abdullah Shafique skips down the track and lofts it over mid on for a boundary.
Flighted delivery, outside off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.

Century in both innings for Imam-ul-Haq! He becomes the tenth Pakistani player to achieve this feat! Tossed up, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq skips down and looks to go downtown. It goes off the outer half of the blade over mid off and the batters take two runs. Terrific innings from the southpaw!
Flatter ball, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq cuts it to cover.
On a length, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq lets it be.
Fuller and on middle. Imam-ul-Haq drives it down to long off for a single.
Flatter and quicker, on a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique defends it off the back foot.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it off the front foot.
Chopped on, nearly! Flatter ball, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq dabs it onto the deck off the bottom half of the blade. The ball goes just past the leg stump.
Darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq tucks it to square leg.
Flatter ball, on a length, on leg. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it around the corner and takes a quick single.
Floated, on a length, on middle. Abdullah Shafique stays back and wrists it to short leg.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Abdullah Shafique stretches forward and keeps it out.
Floated, around middle. Abdullah Shafique tucks it to deep mid-wicket for a run.
On middle, defended.
Tossed up on middle, this is pushed down to long off for one.
Flatter and on middle, this is played back to the bowler.
On middle, this one stays low! It is pushed down to long on for one.
Another one as this is eased down to long off.
A run to end! On off, this is pushed to long off.
Slower and outside off, easy leave.
Another one outside off, not played at.
Flatter and outside off, Imam is happy to leave it alone.
4 leaves in a row as Imam yet again does not fiddle with this one outside off.
On off, defended.
Outside off, left alone again.
FOUR! Starc should have done better, the big man is probably tired. Shorter and outside off, this is cut towards point. Starc there dives over the ball and it goes to the fence.
Tossed up on middle, defended.
On off, this is pushed to cover.
On middle, this is worked through square leg for one.
On off, Imam defends it out.
Another one on the stumps, kept out.
A single as this is played through covers.
On off, it is kept out.
Outside off again, not played at.
On middle, defended.
Down the leg side, left alone.
Outside off, another leave.
Tossed up, on off. Abdullah Shafique blocks it.
Fuller in length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique drives it to the man at extra cover.
Slower through the air, around off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Flatter ball, around leg. Abdullah Shafique nudges it around the corner and rotates the strike.
Floated, on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq tucks it to square leg.
This is darted on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq turns it to square leg.
Tosses it up, outside off. Abdullah Shafique drives it to mid off for a single.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
Floated, full and on off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it out.
Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq cuts it wide of deep cover and collects a couple of runs.
Around off, blocked out.
An overpitched ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq drills it to long on and retains the strike by taking a run.
Tosses it up, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq drives it to mid on and takes a run.
Floated, full and on middle. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
FOUR! Fantastic use of the feet! Tossed up, on a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique shimmies down the track and lofts it over extra cover to bag a boundary.
FOUR! SMASHED! A half-tracker this time from Marnus Labuschagne, around middle. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and pulls it wide of long on for another boundary.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Abdullah Shafique prods and drives it to sweeper cover for one run.
Flighted ball, around off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it out.
Tossed up, around off. Abdullah Shafique stretches forward to defend but he gets an inside edge onto his pad.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Abdullah Shafique rocks back and slaps it towards the extra cover fielder.
Tosses it up nicely, outside off. Abdullah Shafique prods to block it.
Floated, full and outside off. Abdullah Shafique keeps it out.
Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique punches it through the point region and collects a couple of runs.
A loopy ball, around off. Abdullah Shafique prods and defends it.
Tossed up, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq lunges forward to block it.
Fuller in length, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq defends it.
Tossed up, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq drills it to long on for a single.
Tosses it up, on leg. Abdullah Shafique pushes it to long on for a run.
A loopy ball, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq defends it solidly.
Floated, around off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it out to cover.
Flatter ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique punches it to long on for a run.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
A quicker ball, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq does not bother playing at that one.
Floated, on a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq defends it off the front foot.
Tossed up, around off. Imam-ul-Haq gets forward and pushes it to cover.
Floats it up, around off. Imam-ul-Haq lunges forward and keeps it out.
Flatter ball, around leg. Abdullah Shafique whacks it towards square leg and takes a run.
Flatter ball, around leg. Imam-ul-Haq nudges it around the corner and rotates the strike.
Flatter ball, on middle. Abdullah Shafique pushes it back to the bowler.
An overpitched ball, on middle. Abdullah Shafique tucks it to the leg side for a single.
Floated, on a length, around off. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.
Khawaja tosses it up, around off. Imam-ul-Haq gets forward and blocks it. That is it! The players shake hands and the match has ended in a DRAW!
